{
  "stem": "24231.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we always used to sit in front of our house and speak to the people around because-- the Christian people-- because they knew my father.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father grew up with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I grew up with my friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they stopped and we were just BS-ing, or talking, talking around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But one day we were sitting after eight o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oh, during this time, nobody bothered us after eight o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this one day, my father's friend, who joined the Czech [NON-ENGLISH] it was a Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A friend.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father had one time loaned money to to go into business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All of a sudden, he came to, to-- in front of-- to my father and he says, get out, you, you lousy Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Get inside the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my father, at that time, swore that when he comes back, if he ever-- you know, if he ever survives this, this mess, he's going to do something to him, And--",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall the year, exactly the year, but it was not long after, after the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you tried always-- I used to-- I was very conscious of it and I would always try to put books over it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, sometimes you got stopped with SS men, and, and they would just kick you out from the, from the trolley cars or wherever you were.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Well, what happened is I recall, we used to-- this was in, I think, it was March when they came in 1938.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "March or-- it was beginning of the spring.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the radio-- we had the radio on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, the, the German troops are marching to Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every-- I recall that my mother was crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
